    "en": {
      "title": "Father Jiwanta himself withdraws the petition",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Father Jivantha Peiris withdrew the fundamental rights petition that Father Jeevantha Peiris submitted to the Supreme Court to issue an interim order preventing his arrest.",
        "This petition was taken into consideration by a Supreme Court bench consisting of Mr. Priyantha Jayawardene, Mr. Yasanta Kodagoda and Mr. Arjuna Obeysekera.",
        "President's lawyer Mr. Rienzi Arsakularatne appeared before the court on behalf of the petitioner."
      ],
